message.content: This paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computational Linguistics). Other likely sub-categories could include "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), and "cs.DL" (Deep Learning), as these are all relevant areas for research on semantic parsing and question answering. The reasoning for these choices is based on the keywords and topics discussed in the paper, as well as the general focus of research in these sub-categories.
